%H A396509 Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, <a href="https://mathworld.wolfram.com/LambertW-Function.html">Lambert W-Function</a>.
%F A396509 E.g.f.: exp(-1/2 * LambertW(-4*x)).
%F A396509 E.g.f.: B(x)^2, where B(x) is the e.g.f. of A052774.
%F A396509 E.g.f. A(x) satisfies:
